This box is by far the best radio that i&#39;ve ever built.  Just got this  
back from the field, so i decided to re-work the circuit.

It is very unique, clear and conversational.  The box gets good  reception 
and the speaker can really crank.  The adjustable sweep is  erratic, but 
when they speak....you know it !

Have a listen and let me know what you guys think.  I have jumper  wires 
everywhere on the board, the pads were all screwed up.  When ever i  have a 
really badly messed up board to work with, they end up being the best  radios.

-Steve 




